* If you use XPDL prototype, please cite the following paper:

	Christoph Kessler, Lu Li, Aras Atalar, Alin Dobre:
	XPDL: Extensible Platform Description Language to Support Energy Modeling and Optimization.
	Proc. 44th International Conference on Parallel Processing Workshops, ICPP-EMS Embedded Multicore Systems, 
	in conjunction with ICPP-2015, Beijing, 1-4 sep. 2015, pp. 51-60, IEEE. DOI 10.1109/ICPPW.2015.17

