------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation:

1. Install xerces (tested on 3.2.1)
	https://xerces.apache.org/xerces-c/

2. add YOUR_XERCES_DIRECTORY/lib to LD_LIBRARY_PATH

3. add the following line to .bashrc with XPDL_HOME set to be the root folder of XPDL software

	export XPDL_HOME=YOUR_XPDL_PATH
	export PATH=$XPDL_HOME/bin:$PATH

4. go to src/

5. change the xerces installation directory in Makefile

6. make

7. make run
	Compile the xpdl file in the XPDL example folder
	This will also open the xpdl_compiler generated hpp file directly
